{"tid":500083,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)白宮仆直 爭女特務王 末日先鋒","createTime":"2017-12-15T12:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T13:58:34.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"96efbe1be9854c825716721c2df1e30072c2e54b","tid":500083,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:42:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=WrSUBKq8f2q0wBOzjsttpJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=7db8a261\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=WrSUBKq8f2q0wBOzjsttpJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=eb87eff8\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/5/5d/White_House_Down_poster_with_billing_block.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F5%2F5d%2FWhite_House_Down_poster_with_billing_block.jpg&h=0de00aa8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/55/This_Means_War_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F55%2FThis_Means_War_Poster.jpg&h=28d6f670&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/fb/Mad_Max_Fury_Road_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ffb%2FMad_Max_Fury_Road_poster.jpg&h=81d7d072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.宣揚和平主義的美國總統詹姆士&middot;索耶爲了結束長久以來的中東戰爭而親自前往伊朗表示和平，聲言他會把所有部署在中東地區的美軍全部撤出，將自己的提案交給其他國家審核。約翰&middot;凱爾是一名在阿富汗服過兵役的美軍中士，因爲行爲不檢被革除後去當國會警察，成為美國眾議院議長伊萊&middot;拉弗森的私人護衛。而約翰好不容易得到一次美國特勤局的面試機會，並與自己關係不好的女兒愛蜜莉一同前去白宮。面試時，特勤隊副主任卡蘿&middot;菲妮提因為看不上約翰的狼藉簡歷而拒絕了他，而失落的約翰為了保住面子而只能故意騙女兒說自己已被錄取；父女倆隨後加入了一個白宮參觀團..<br />\n<br />\n2.故事敘述美國中情局的兩位頂尖探員塔克（湯姆&middot;哈迪 飾）和FDR（克里斯&middot;潘恩 飾）在事業和生活都是密不可分的哥們，在陰錯陽差下同時愛上事業有成的女強人蘿拉（瑞絲&middot;薇斯朋 飾），雙方發現後決定公平競爭，過程中使出所有中情局探員本領竊聽、偷拍只為了博得蘿拉歡心，當中也因此導致兄弟反目，蘿拉也在兩人之中無法作出決定<br />\n<br />\n3.在不遠的未來，人類文明因為核爆崩落後成為了荒漠世界，土壤酸化、沒有法治和憐憫，水和石油是珍貴的資源。前澳大利亞公路巡警麥斯一開始被軍閥領導的不死老喬手下的「戰爭男孩」捕獲，車子「XB攔截者」也被奪走並被帶到了不死老喬統治的「西方堡壘」；西方堡壘是一個富有綠意和水資源的峽谷形軍闊，但貧民只能待在堡壘下方讓老喬釋放的地下水來維生。麥斯被剪了頭髮並被判定為「強效型供血者」，作為半死不活的戰爭男孩奈克斯的「血袋」。同時，不死老喬在堡壘上放下了水給下面的貧民們..<br />\n<br />\n9 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=WrSUBKq8f2q0wBOzjsttpJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=9869ef6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=WrSUBKq8f2q0wBOzjsttpJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=2e5095d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bba822053d8ee83ae7c2c2d07d213a3fddfb9c3","tid":500083,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T12:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid